pageProduct.name: OsteVit-D Vitamin D3 250 Tablets
pageProduct.description:
General Information

OsteVit-D One-A-Day Vitamin D3 1000IU enhances calcium absorption to maintain strong bones and comes in a small, easy to swallow tablet format.

OsteVit-D One-A-Day Vitamin D3 Tablets enhances calcium absorption and maintains strong bones & muscle function.
The small, easy to swallow tablet can be crushed if required.

Size: 250 Tablets

KEY FEATURES

• • Enhances Calcium absorbtion
• • Maintains bone density and strength
• • Supports bone health and muscle function
• • Supports healthy immune system function
• • Small, easy to swallow tablets can be crushed if required

Warnings

Vitamins can only be of assistance if dietary vitamin intake is inadequate.
Contains lactose
Contains sugar

Ingredients

Acacia, dl-alpha-tocopherol, lactose monohydrate, magnesium stearate, maize starch, medium chain triglycerides, microcrystalline cellulose, silicon dioxide, sucrose

Active Ingredients: Contains Vitamin D3 1000IU (cholecalciferol 25 micrograms) per tablet

Directions

Adults and children over 12 years of age: One tablet daily or as directed by your healthcare professional. Tablets may be crushed if required. For children under 12 years of age OsteVit-D Children's Oral Drops are recommended.

STORAGE INSTRUCTIONS

Store below 25°C
